@{
    ViewBag.Title = "Home Page";
}

<!-- Header -->
<header id="headerwrap" class="fullheight">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="intro-text">
            <div class="intro-lead-in wow bounceInDown" data-wow-delay="0.5s">We clean <span class="wodry">Wood|Cement|Plastic|Anything!</span></div>
            <div class="intro-heading wow bounceInUp" data-wow-delay="1s">Vicks Vase <span class="thin">Cleaners</span></div>
            <a href="#about-us" class="page-scroll btn btn-xl btn-negative  wow bounceInDown" data-wow-delay="2s">Tell Me More <i class="fa fa-angle-down fa-2x"></i></a>
        </div>
    </div>
</header>

<!-- About Section -->
<section id="about-us">
    <div class="section-inner">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-12 text-center wow fadeInDown">
                    <h2 class="section-heading"><strong>About</strong> Us</h2>
                    <h3 class="section-subheading text-muted">Vase cleaning? Why would I need that?</h3>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row gap">
                <div class="col-md-4 wow fadeInLeft">
                    <img src="~/Content/assets/img/Vasesketch.jpg" class="img-responsive" />
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-8 wow fadeInRight">
                    <br />
                    <br />
                    <p>So you're sitting there asking yourself, "Why would I need somebody to clean my vase? Can't I just do it myself?". Well let us tell you. You're flat out wrong! Here at Vicks Vase Cleaners we offer deep vase cleaning for all our customers. You can't find a better vase cleanery than us!</p>
                    <p>
                        People ask us all the time, why make a service that seems pointless as people can probably do this simple task themseleves. We tell them, great question.
                        <br />
                        <br />
                        So come on down and let us clean your vase! Packages start at at $120 plus tax.
                        We do not clean bowls, please stop asking.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

