<!-- Services Section -->
<section id="services">
    <div class="section-inner">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-12 text-center wow fadeInDown">
                    <h2 class="section-heading"><strong>Our</strong> Services</h2>
                    <h3 class="section-subheading text-muted">Here we offer three amazing packages</h3>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row wow fadeInUp">
                <div class="col-md-4 service-item">
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-md-2 col-sm-2 col-xs-2 service-icon">
                            <i class="pe-7s-video fa-4x"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-10 col-sm-10 col-xs-10 pull-right">
                            <h4 class="service-heading">Basic Cleaning: $120 + Tax</h4>
                            <p class="text-muted">Our Mixologist will create a special, custom blend of soaps and fragrences made just for your vase. They look at the structure and material to best design a custom cleaner for your vase and your vase alone. We then have our lead Clean Designer map a cleaning path for you vase using only the most advanced cleaning techniques</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4 service-item">
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-md-2 col-sm-2 col-xs-2 service-icon">
                            <i class="pe-7s-phone fa-4x"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-10 col-sm-10 col-xs-10 pull-right">
                            <h4 class="service-heading">Advanced Package: $250 + Tax</h4>
                            <p class="text-muted">Our advanced package includes everything from our basic package, but includes a vase profile for your vase made by our in-house Vase Photographer. The profile will include a detailed list of atomic make up of your vase to help you will future care. The profile will be leather-bound, a booking for the advanced package will allow you to make a reservation* for one of our location, even if they are filled for the day!
                            <br />
                            <br />
                            *this is subject to cancelation if we feel like it.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4 service-item">
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-md-2 col-sm-2 col-xs-2 service-icon">
                            <i class="pe-7s-tools fa-4x"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-10 col-sm-10 col-xs-10 pull-right">
                            <h4 class="service-heading">Le Meilleure: $500 + Tax</h4>
                            <p class="text-muted">Details of this package are only told in person, however this does include all things detailed in the previous packages.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

